ets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差政府錢咪通緝，下次入境就立即扣人</blockquote><br />\n港共政府會咁做就唔叫港共政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但香港有大把on9真係信告唔到旅客<br />\n<br />\n民智未開，枉稱國際城市"},{"pid":"6d908e001175031d00a0e7d3c544a71ac940667c","tid":223203,"uid":51840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:54:40.000Z","msg":"警察唔做嘢？非指定地點露營唔係要告嘅咩？"},{"pid":"4f362dd1b44ab881166cb3114f269a4e536aa47e","tid":223203,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛..租間屋幾舊水都比唔起?"},{"pid":"bb5e0b22ee33e9c0f9448707a84f373b9d6132fb","tid":223203,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:55:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警察唔做嘢？非指定地點露營唔係要告嘅咩？</blockquote><br />\n有法神話無身份證無得告"},{"pid":"ba226600dd90af76375b335490f292071eaae6ab","tid":223203,"uid":30593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:57:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>警察唔做嘢？非指定地點露營唔係要告嘅咩？</blockquote><br />\n有法神話無身份證無得告</blockquote><br />\n唔係無得告<br />\n係唔會告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c40c49a93643d62c0cd528ee797294d4dbfad4a","tid":223203,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T08:01:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>警察唔做嘢？非指定地點露營唔係要告嘅咩？</blockquote><br />\n有法神話無身份證無得告</blockquote><br />\n唔係無得告<br />\n係唔會告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港有今日係比班on9法神累<br />\n<br />\n自己唔曉就9up<br />\n幫政府n重標準護航"}]}